* Before Watchmen: "Dr Manhattan" volume upgraded to fully hi-res contents; all    *
*                  major volumes re-wrapped to add the 2013 Deluxe Edition covers. *
************************************************************************************


   Contains:

BEFORE WATCHMEN - All 37 issues in Digital Hi-Res, compiled into 9 pseudo-TPBs.
Sorted by narrative chronology, which may (or may not) be taken as a suggested
reading order. Plus "The Curse of the Crimson Corsair", which collects the entire
56-page story-within-a-story from the first 28 issues. Each bookended with three
collection cover variants, in addition to the complete single-issue cover galleries.

WATCHMEN - The original graphic novel, compiled into a single pseudo-TPD from the
Digital Hi-Res re-releases. Plus "Under the Hood" and "Minutes", collecting ~100
pages of back matter from the original and the enhanced 2005 editions, respectively.

MOTION COMIC - 12 x ~25 minutes, ca 640x360, XviD.
